  "commentary": "With SPX at 6834.68 sitting just below the 6840 GEX flip, dealers are in PIN regime and likely adding long hedges into any upside moves, creating natural resistance as we approach the massive +29.6B gamma wall at 6850. The proximity to flip (only 5 handles away) means dealers will aggressively sell any push above 6840 and buy any dip toward the 6820 negative gamma zone, creating a tight trading range. Watch for rejection at 6840-6845 resistance cluster and support at 6820 where dealers flip to amplifying mode.\n\nBottom line: expect price to chop between 6820-6850 with dealers capping rallies.",
